original_title: Carrera de bicicletas en el velódromo de arroyo seco
overview: A record of a bicycle race held at the Arroyo Seco velodrome, which was located in the Quinta de Iglesias street (modern day Agraciada) by Entre Ríos, Zapicán and San Fructuoso.
title: Bicycle Race at the Arroyo Seco Cycle Track
